# Component Folders

```
src/components/
  ui/            # shadcn/ui primitives (managed by `npx shadcn add`)
  layout/        # Header, Footer, navigation shell
  calculator/    # Asset forms, stepper, summary, results display
  shared/        # ThemeToggle, PriceBar, reusable widgets
  providers/     # ThemeProvider, context providers
```

- Do not put custom components directly in `ui/` — that folder is for shadcn primitives.
- Do not dump components in `src/components/` root — pick the right subfolder.
- Calculator-specific components (forms, results) go in `calculator/`.
- Shared components used across pages go in `shared/`.
